\'93Then we\'92ll find him in the state section.\'94\
\'93Why are we whispering?\'94 Taggert whispered back.\
\'93Because I don\'92t want the dead to hear me,\'94 Roderick replied.\
\'93Do you think there are more of them in here?\'94 Hargrave asked.\
Roderick paused a moment to look back at the ravaged prison guard, and gave a meaningful nod to Hargrave and Taggert.\
\'93I don\'92t think he chewed his own head off,\'94 Roderick answered. \'93Do you?\'94\
